ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS, in order to add an exemption to the obligation to obtain a temporary resident visa for British Subjects who have the right of abode (live, work and vote) in the United Kingdom. The technical amendments update references made to government and territorial entities and simplify the French text.
